snippet.title: Darkest Dungeon 2: Road of Ruin - Official Early Access Trailer
snippet.description:
Ride out on a desperate journey to avert the apocalypse in the upcoming rogue-like gothic horror RPG, Darkest Dungeon II. Check out the trailer for a look at gameplay and more. 

Early Access for the game begins on October 26, 2021.

#IGN #DarkestDungeonII
